        <h1 class="h1 text-uppercase mt-3">History of soroban</h1>
    		<p class="lead text-justify text-indent">For more than 26 centuries, Greeks used marble boxes to calculate commodity transactions. These cans were later published between the eastern and central regions of the Roman Empire.</p>
				<p class="lead text-justify text-indent">A box with sand or fine dust was then used to draw lines with sticks or fingers to perform calculations. It seems that the Chinese later succeeded in forming a different type of their abacus (SUAN PAN), a box with chopsticks bearing 5 lower and 2 upper beads.</p>
				<hr>
				<figure class="figure">
					<img class="figure-img img-thumbnail" src="../../images/suan-pan.png" alt="suan-pan abacus">
					<figcaption class="figure-caption text-dark">Chinese abacus SUAN PAN</figcaption>
				</figure>
				<p class="lead text-justify text-indent">In the end, the Chinese abacus traveled to Japan in the 16th century through trade agreements between them. Japanese studied it for about 300 years and then removed a lower bead and later another superior to reach their own abacus in 1930, which develops intelligence more than others.</p>
				<hr>
				<figure class="figure">
					<img class="figure-img img-thumbnail" src="../../images/abacus.png" alt="soroban abacus">
					<figcaption class="figure-caption text-dark">Japanese abacus SOROBAN</figcaption>
				</figure>
				<p class="lead text-justify text-indent">Recently Soroban has been accredited in the educational programs of many countries to teach in schools for students, and UNESCO has added it to the list of intangible cultural heritage worldwide.</p>
				<hr>
				<h1 class="h1 text-uppercase">objectives of learning SOROBAN</h1>
				<ul class="h5 text-left">
					<li>Develop children's mental abilities.</li>
					<li>Balance between the right and left lobes of the brain.</li>
					<li>Improve the child's attention, speed in reading, writing and self-confidence.</li>
					<li>Acquire many mental talents that will help them forever.</li>
					<li>Develop mental capacity, increase responsiveness and improve memory.</li>
					<li>Increase the number of brain cells used during operations.</li>
					<li>Activates the right lobe of the brain (scientists have discovered in an experiment that the right lobe has recorded a strong electrical activity, when placed under the device of a brain electrical diagram while the mental calculation of the user by the perception of the abacus).</li>
					<li>Perform various calculations, regardless of size or complexity.</li>
					<li>The maturation of children's mathematics.</li>
					<li>The use of the sense of hearing and the sense of sight, attract the attention of the learner, which gives him a great ability to concentrate.</li>
					<li>Prevents aging of the brain and Alzheimer's disease. In fact, during the movement of the fingers on the beads of the abacus, the influx of blood into the brain has been observed. That's why we organize Soroban classes in Japan for the elderly.</li>
					<li>The SOROBAN program is a meaningful and educational ground for the child, and instead of leaving it to negative influences, such as TV and video games, the child plays the program and really takes a fun time learning.</li>
